&lt;큰일인데… 이제 료슈도 탐정놀이에 흥미가 떨어지기 시작했나 봐…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Ah, no... Looks like Ryōshū's getting tired of playing detective...&gt;

KR:
&lt;일단 돌아갈까? 증거를 찾으면 그때 다시 와도…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Why don't we leave for now? We can always come back here once we uncover more evidence.&gt;

KR:
&lt;…아지트 위치는 알아뒀으니까, 나중에 다시 오자.&gt;
EN:
&lt;Well, we now know where the Yurodiviye are. We can always come back here if we ever need anything else.&gt;
